 for she said, “God has appointed for me another offspring instead of Abel, for Cain killed him.”"}, {:version=>"Berean Study Bible", :text=>"And Adam again had relations with his wife, and she gave birth to a son and named him Seth, saying, “God has granted me another seed in place of Abel, since Cain killed him.”"}, {:version=>"New American Standard Bible ", :text=>"Adam had relations with his wife again; and she gave birth to a son, and named him Seth, for, she said, \"God has appointed me another offspring in place of Abel, for Cain killed him.\""}, {:version=>"New King James Version", :text=>"And Adam knew his wife again, and she bore a son and named him Seth, “For God has appointed another seed for me instead of Abel, whom Cain killed.”"}, {:version=>"King James Bible", :text=>"And Adam knew his wife again; and she bare a son, and called his name Seth: For God, "}, {:version=>", hath appointed me another seed instead of Abel, whom Cain slew.", :text=>"Christian Standard Bible"}, {:version=>"Adam was intimate with his wife again, and she gave birth to a son and named him Seth, for she said, \"God has given me another child in place of Abel, since Cain killed him.\"", :text=>"Contemporary English Version"}, {:version=>"Adam and his wife had another son. They named him Seth, because they said, \"God has given us a son to take the place of Abel, who was killed by his brother Cain.\" ", :text=>"Good News Translation"}, {:version=>"Adam and his wife had another son. She said, \"God has given me a son to replace Abel, whom Cain killed.\" So she named him Seth. ", :text=>"Holman Christian Standard Bible"}, {:version=>"Adam was intimate with his wife again, and she gave birth to a son and named him Seth, for she said, \"God has given me another child in place of Abel, since Cain killed him.\" ", :text=>"International Standard Version"}, {:version=>"Later on, after Adam had sexual relations with his wife, she gave birth to a son and named him Seth, because \"God granted me another offspring to replace Abel, since Cain murdered him.\"", :text=>"NET Bible"}, {:version=>"And Adam had marital relations with his wife again, and she gave birth to a son. She named him Seth, saying, \"God has given me another child in place of Abel because Cain killed him.\"", :text=>"New Heart English Bible"}, {:version=>"Adam had marital relations with his wife again, and she gave birth to a son, and named him Seth, \"for God has appointed me another child instead of Abel, for Cain killed him.\"", :text=>"GOD'S WORD® Translation"}, {:version=>"Adam made love to his wife again. She gave birth to a son and named him Seth, because [she said,] \"God has given me another child in place of Abel, since Cain killed him.\" ", :text=>"JPS Tanakh 1917"}, {:version=>"And Adam knew his wife again; and she bore a son, and called his name  Seth: 'for God  hath appointed me another seed instead of Abel; for Cain slew him.'", :text=>"New American Standard 1977 "}, {:version=>"And Adam had relations with his wife again; and she gave birth to a son, and named him Seth, for, ", :text=>" “God has appointed me another offspring in place of Abel; for Cain killed him.”"}, {:version=>"King James 2000 Bible", :text=>"And Adam knew his wife again; and she bore a son, and called his name Seth: For God, said she, has appointed me another child instead of Abel, whom Cain slew."}, {:version=>"American King James Version", :text=>"And Adam knew his wife again; and she bore a son, and called his name Seth: For God, said she, has appointed me another seed instead of Abel, whom Cain slew."}, {:version=>"American Standard Version", :text=>"And Adam knew his wife again; and she bare a son, and called his name Seth. For,'said she , God hath appointed me another seed instead of Abel; for Cain slew him."}, {:version=>"Brenton Septuagint Translation", :text=>"And Adam knew Eve his wife, and she conceived and bore a son, and called his name Seth, saying, For God has raised up to me another seed instead of Abel, whom Cain slew."}, {:version=>"Douay-Rheims Bible", :text=>"Adam also knew his wife again: and she brought forth a son, and called his name Seth, saying: God hath given me another seed, for Abel whom Cain slew. "}, {:version=>"Darby Bible Translation", :text=>"And Adam knew his wife again, and she bore a son, and called his name Seth: ... For God has appointed me another seed instead of Abel, because Cain has slain him."}, {:version=>"English Revised Version", :text=>"And Adam knew his wife again; and she bare a son, and called his name Seth: For, said she, God hath appointed me another seed instead of Abel; for Cain slew him."}, {:version=>"Webster's Bible Translation", :text=>"And Adam knew his wife again, and she bore a son, and called his name Seth: For God, said she, hath appointed me another seed instead of Abel, whom Cain slew."}, {:version=>"World English Bible", :text=>"Adam knew his wife again. She gave birth to a son, and named him Seth, \"for God has appointed me another child instead of Abel, for Cain killed him.\""}, {:version=>"Young's Literal Translation", :text=>" And Adam again knoweth his wife, and she beareth a son, and calleth his name Seth, 'for God hath appointed for me another seed instead of Abel:' for Cain had slain him."}]}